snippet.title: The Sims™ 2 Nightlife Official Trailer
snippet.description: Send your Sims on an epic night out!  Whether they're dancing until dawn, romancing that special someone, or striking out at the bowling alley, it'll be an unforgettable night.  Get more info at www.TheSims2.com.
